Output demo/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Molokai"
Set FontSize 18
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "cd /Users/adam/projects/zeroboot/zeroboot/demo && source venv/bin/activate && clear"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Type "python agent.py"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "What's faster for matrix multiplication: nested loops, list comprehension, numpy, or map/reduce?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 55s

Type "exit"
Enter
Sleep 3s
